# .lycheeignore
#
# URL patterns that lychee should skip when checking links in doc/ and *.md.
# Add patterns here for hosts that are auth-walled, rate-limited, or known to
# return transient errors for unauthenticated HEAD/GET requests.
#
# One pattern per line. Supports glob-style wildcards.
# Full docs: https://lychee.cli.rs/usage/ignoring/

# GitHub login/auth walls (linked repos are public but auth redirects happen)
https://github.com/login*

# pub.dev search and analytics pages (rate-limited for CI IPs)
https://pub.dev/packages*

# Localhost and loopback references in code samples
http://localhost*
http://127.0.0.1*
